metadata.name: OwnPass #1
metadata.description: OwnPass is 3D NFT of six characters in the Aotu worlds 。Aotu worlds 2D NFT holders can convert into 3DNFT through official activities.Six roles:King；Grey；Kalie；Phantom·S；Lemon；Daniel。In particular, they are not only Genesis 3D for the IP of the concave-convex world, but also the Genesis Pass card for the whole OwnVerse.Genesis 3D has only introduced 6 characters, and there are 30 subsequent 3D characters。
